Empath::

The black-and-yellow femme nods and heads outside, changing to her 
favored jet mode and taking off.  She doesn't take a direct course 
for her objective just yet, favoring an oblique approach.  (For those 
of you who don't know such obscure words, "oblique" refers to a 
moderately shallow arc.)

OOC: For those who went into the "New Ideas" discussion topic on the 
site, this is my Soul Orb concept.  For those who never saw it, let's 
just say these are Vok artifacts with great powers for those lucky 
few capable of activating them: Meteara, Owlhawk, Empath, Rodimus 
Prime, Skulletron, and Phoenix.  More names may be added to this 
list, eventually.  They need to have a notable quirk, and not just in 
bodily construction or personality.
